  "title": "Architectural Coordinator",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Job Description</strong></u></p>\n<p>· Assist the Planning Manager to coordinate design detailing between Clients and Consultants</p>\n<p>· Review, update and coordinate all architectural work including shop drawings for the project</p>\n<p>· Resolve all site architectural issues and implement the right methods to ensure quality and productivity, using BIM software or equivalent.</p>\n<p>· Liaise and coordinate with sub-contractors and vendors on projects and work</p>\n<p>· Ensure compliance with Architectural specifications, and achieve quality aspect of architectural works without deviation to authority requirements</p>\n<p>· Carry out architectural works scheduling, material requisition, cost control, project supervision and documentation in accordance to Master Programme</p>\n<p>· Review project specifications, tender clarifications and construction drawings for Contract/Procurement management</p>\n<p>. Requires experience in site coordination (arrangement of site work, material delivery, mock up, samples, quality control etc) for architectural trade</p>",
